  "reference_number": "SYR0421",
  "remarks": "\nThe Secretary of State considers that there are reasonable grounds to suspect that Sayf BOULAD is an involved person under the Syria (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 on the basis of the following ground: BOULAD is or has been involved in repressing the civilian population of Syria and, during the civil war, the commission of violations of international humanitarian law. \n",
